<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 28 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵呵，<delay20 />今天是期待已久的
烟花大会～<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />到晚上7点还有一段时间，<delay20 />
在此之前，<delay8 />得先把打扫卫生之类的杂事
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />都搞定才行呢！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 28 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在广场上摆出小吃摊，<delay8 />
庆典氛围就会高涨起来呢～<pageBreak /><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />对了对了，<delay20 />抽奖是从晚上7点开始吧。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />希望<tag a="110" b="4" />你<delay8 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也能获得好东西！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 28 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天一整天好像都是大晴天，<delay8 />
是放烟花的绝佳天气！<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在夜空中绽放的盛大烟花<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我现在就期待不已。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一想到烟花大会马上就要开始了，<delay8 />
我就心神不宁呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，
你也很期待吧？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不是只有我这样就好～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00">我<delay20 />最喜欢
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />烟花燃放前的<delay8 />
心跳与兴奋感了～
<anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />开始燃放之后，<delay8 />就会为烟花升空的声音
兴奋不已～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Aha" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />再过一会儿，就要开始放烟花了哦！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />传统的烟花也很美，<delay20 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过，<delay20 />稍显奇特的烟花，
我也挺喜欢的。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />烟花放完后，<delay8 />
总感觉比平时的夜晚更加安静呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过，像这样闭上眼睛，<delay20 />
在夜空中盛放的巨大烟花
仍残留在眼前呢～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />烟花的光芒与响声激荡人心<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />为了不忘记这份感动，<delay8 />
<anim id="Assent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />得在日记中写下来才行。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在烟花放完之后，<delay20 />
我感到有一点孤单。<pageBreak /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过，和<tag a="110" b="4" />你聊了聊，<delay20 />
孤单落寞的感觉
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就一扫而空了！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 29 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今年最后一次烟花大会<delay20 />
终于结束了呢～<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />希望明年，
我也能在<tag a="110" b="33" />
看烟花呢。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 29 00 00 00 00">虽然大会结束了，<delay20 />
<anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但我看到了很多烟花，
非常幸福！
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="90" b="27" />年的烟花会留在我的心里，<delay20 />
而我现在就开始期待明年的烟花了。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我<delay20 />是不是太贪心了呢？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="012" attrib="00 00 00 29 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天的烟花大会，<delay8 />
作为收场来说真是太精彩了<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在烟花谢幕后感到落寞是人之常情，<delay20 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我却觉得心旷神怡，很奇异呢。<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>